README
=====

1. Compilation
Enter the source directory and issue make.

2. Running
The make command will create an executable 'reversi'. To run the game, enter

$ ./reversi <ip address of server> <port> [search depth]

The paramter search depth is optional. If this paramter is not specified,
 it will be set to a default value of 7.

Example invocation:

$ ./reversi 10.15.24.161 5001 8

$ ./reversi 10.15.24.161 5001
